      <div class="why-choose-us__text">Talk to real people who care. Our support team is always here to help — no bots, no fuss.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="why-choose-us__feature">
      <div class="why-choose-us__icon">
        <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/your-store-id/files/eco-icon.svg" alt="Eco Icon">
      </div>
      <div class="why-choose-us__heading">Sustainable Products</div>
